<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>indexing on 碼農生活</title><link>https://doggor.github.io/tags/indexing/</link><description>Recent content in indexing on 碼農生活</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cmn-Hans</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2019 11:00:41 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://doggor.github.io/tags/indexing/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>暫停MySQL索引更新和參照檢查</title><link>https://doggor.github.io/posts/2019/stop-mysql-indexing-and-reference-checking/</link><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2019 11:00:41 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://doggor.github.io/posts/2019/stop-mysql-indexing-and-reference-checking/</guid><description>&lt;p>在MySQL數據庫處理資料時，InnoDB會為每行資料逐一檢查其外鍵(Foreign Key Check)，而MyISAM則更新表格索引(Indexing)，對於大量的資料滙入或更新會帶來更長的執行時間。這時我們更希望是在所有資料寫入以後才一次性地進行檢查和索引更新。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>